item.title: RALLY AWARDS
item.description: Double Irish Rally champion Donagh Kelly and the renowned motorsport commentator Dougie Hughes are the special guests of Skibbereen and District Car Club for Saturday night’s PlasticBags.ie Southern 4 Rally Championship and the Carbery Plastics Skibbereen & District Car Club Championship awards ceremony.

item.title: Launch of the 2016 Plasticbags.ie Southern 4 Rally Championship.
item.description: The launch of the Plasticbags.ie Southern 4 Rally Championship took place at the home of Plasticbags.ie in Annacotty Business Park, Co Limerick on Sunday last.

item.title: Awards Ceremony
item.description: The Skibbereen and District Car Club will honour its championship award winners at a ceremony at the Celtic Ross Hotel, Rosscarbery on Saturday January 23rd next. The recipients of the main awards for the Carbery Plastics Skibbereen and District Car Club Championship are Bandon’s Victor Beamish (Drivers’ category) and Lisavaird’s Mark McCarthy
